---
---

<section class="ai-section">
	<div class="section-content">
		<div class="section-icon">
			<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
				<rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2"/>
				<path d="M9 9h6v6H9z"/>
				<path d="M9 1v2M15 1v2M9 21v2M15 21v2M20 9h2M20 15h2M1 9h2M1 15h2"/>
				<circle cx="12" cy="12" r="1.5" fill="currentColor"/>
			</svg>
		</div>
		<h2>Custom AI Solutions</h2>
		<p class="section-description">
			Practical AI integration tailored to your business needs. From intelligent automation 
			to custom model deployment—solving real problems, not chasing hype.
		</p>
		<div class="capabilities">
			<div class="capability">
				<h3>LLM Integration</h3>
				<p>Custom chatbots, RAG pipelines, and knowledge bases. Integrate OpenAI, Anthropic, or open-source models into your existing workflows.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="capability">
				<h3>Model Deployment</h3>
				<p>Self-hosted inference with vLLM, Ollama, or custom inference servers. GPU optimization and scaling strategies.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="capability">
				<h3>AI Infrastructure</h3>
				<p>MLOps pipelines, vector databases, and data preprocessing pipelines. Production-ready AI systems that scale.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.ai-section {
		padding: 4rem 0;
		border-top: 1px solid rgb(var(--gray-light));
	}

	.section-content {
		text-align: center;
	}

	.section-icon {
		width: 64px;
		height: 64px;
		margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
		color: var(--accent);
	}

	.section-icon svg {
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
	}

	h2 {
		font-size: 2rem;
		margin: 0 0 1rem;
	}

	.section-description {
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		color: rgb(var(--gray-dark));
		max-width: 600px;
		margin: 0 auto 2rem;
	}

	.capabilities {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
		gap: 1.5rem;
		text-align: left;
	}

	.capability {
		background: var(--bg-color);
		border: 1px solid rgb(var(--gray-light));
		border-radius: 12px;
		padding: 1.5rem;
		transition: all 0.3s ease;
	}

	.capability:hover {
		border-color: var(--accent);
		transform: translateY(-4px);
		box-shadow: var(--box-shadow);
	}

	.capability h3 {
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
		color: rgb(var(--black));
	}

	.capability p {
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		color: rgb(var(--gray-dark));
		margin: 0;
		line-height: 1.5;
	}

	@media (max-width: 720px) {
		.capabilities {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}
	}
</style>
